      "title": "Power cut reduced to three hours today: PUCSL",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Electricity Board (CEB) has given the directive to reduce the scheduled power cut for today to three hours, the Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) said.",
        "Accordingly, the areas that come under A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V and W group will experience a two-hour power cut during the daytime and a one-hour in the night.",
        "The areas under group CC will have a two-hour power cut and areas listed under M, N, O, X, Y and Z group will face a three-hour powercut. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
